							<td style='padding: 8px;'>- Defines parsing logic for assignment expressions within the syntax tree, transforming assignment tokens into structured AST nodes<br>- Facilitates variable assignment handling by extracting variable names and values, enabling accurate representation of environment or configuration settings in the overall codebase architecture<br>- Ensures proper integration of assignment statements during parsing, supporting subsequent interpretation or execution phases.</td>
						</tr>
