							<td style='padding: 8px;'>- Defines parsing logic for command-line redirection syntax, enabling the recognition and translation of redirection tokens into abstract syntax tree nodes<br>- Facilitates accurate interpretation of input/output redirection operations within the overall command parsing architecture, ensuring correct handling of file descriptors and redirection types during command execution.</td>
